section.p:
In order to enable faceted search a documentation must have a
        search-facets.json that stores all the possible categories and their
        values. The file is located at this path:
        $out-folder/oxygen-webhelp/app/facets/  Here's what such file should look
        like:{
  "facets": [
    {
      "key": "product",
      "navtitle": "Product",
      "categories": [
        {
          "key": "X2000",
          "navtitle": "X2000 Phone Guide",
          "categories": []
        },
        {
          "key": "X1000",
          "navtitle": "X1000 Phone Guide",
          "categories": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "audience",
      "navtitle": "Audience",
      "categories": [
        {
          "key": "Technician",
          "navtitle": "Technician Levels",
          "categories": [
            {
              "key": "TechnicianOne",
              "navtitle": "Technician Level One",
              "categories": []
            },
            {
              "key": "TechnicianTwo",
              "navtitle": "Technician Level Two",
              "categories": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "key": "BasicUser",
          "navtitle": "Basic User Level",
          "categories": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
 The generation of this file is described in this topic.
